# Dev Log Projects

When starting a new project in the Dev Log:

1. Create a folder: `Docs/Dev Log/<start date> - <project name>/`
   - Date format: `YYYY-MM-DD` (e.g. `2026-03-08`)
   - Project name: short, descriptive title

2. Copy the spec template into the folder:
   - Source: `Docs/Dev Log/Project Spec Template.md`
   - Destination: `Docs/Dev Log/<start date> - <project name>/<project name> Spec.md`

3. Fill out the spec collaboratively with the user:
   - Title line: `# <start date> <project name>`
   - Description: 1-2 sentence goal
   - Scope: what needs this project addresses
   - Steps: concrete checklist of work items with sub-steps

4. Additional project files (notes, logs, artifacts) go in the same folder.
